<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to <%= ENV['APP_NAME'] || 'myApp' %>!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
      
      <p>Thanks for signing up! Please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
      
      <a href="<%= @verification_url %>" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
      
      <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <p><%= @verification_url %></p>
      
      <p>This verification link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
      
      <p>If you didn't create an account, please ignore this email.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The <%= ENV['APP_NAME'] || 'myApp' %> Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
